originalSql:
SELECT 
    t.title AS movie_title,
    p.info AS person_info,
    a.name AS actor_name,
    ka.keyword AS movie_keyword,
    co.name AS company_name,
    ct.kind AS company_type
FROM 
    title t
JOIN 
    complete_cast cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id
JOIN 
    aka_name a ON cc.subject_id = a.person_id
JOIN 
    person_info p ON a.person_id = p.person_id
LEFT JOIN 
    movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
LEFT JOIN 
    keyword ka ON mk.keyword_id = ka.id
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
JOIN 
    company_name co ON mc.company_id = co.id
JOIN 
    company_type ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id
WHERE 
    t.production_year >= 2000
ORDER BY 
    t.production_year DESC, 
    t.title

SELECT COALESCE("title"."title", "title"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "s1"."info" AS "PERSON_INFO", "aka_name"."name" AS "ACTOR_NAME", "keyword"."keyword" AS "MOVIE_KEYWORD", "company_name"."name" AS "COMPANY_NAME", "company_type"."kind" AS "COMPANY_TYPE", "title"."production_year"
FROM "title"
INNER JOIN "complete_cast" ON "title"."id" = "complete_cast"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "aka_name" ON "complete_cast"."subject_id" = "aka_name"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "s1"."person_id"
LEFT JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id"
INNER JOIN "company_type" ON "movie_companies"."company_type_id" = "company_type"."id"
WHERE "title"."production_year" >= 2000
ORDER BY "title"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST, "title"."title"
